# {{lb|en|grammar}} a pronoun that [[replace]]s a [[noun]] whose [[identity]] can be [[understood]] from the [[context]]; it indicates whether the noun is [[singular]] or [[plural]], and whether it is [[near]] or [[far]] from the [[speaker]] or [[writer]]
#: Note: In [[English]] they are the same as the [[demonstrative adjective]]s - [[this]], [[that]], [[these]] and [[those]]

